response.overview: When Genevieve's night takes an unfortunate turn, she knows what she needs to conquer the discomfort: rosemary focaccia and time alone on the couch. She goes out on a mission as she always does. But when she's derailed by an ill-fated stranger and her own conscience, Genevieve makes an unlikely friend and gets an education in the radical act of trying to feel better.
response.title: Ill Feelings
